<span class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/16b679e83631636f3cb74e8d62397330?s=44&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D44&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /></span>
